        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2"> Well I read it here about Furor bitching about focus items, just had a look at the Legacy of Steel site and there are some sniping comments about "throw away all your TOV loot and get some summoned focus items instead." What's the problem? None of these people are casters mind you. How do focus items make loot with 100 mana 100hp tons of int/wis/cha and resists useless? Verant finally get around to giving casters a means to experience a power curve similar to melee who upgrade their gear and now they are all complaining about it. I don't get it.</P><P>Abaraxas Malfoy<BR>Defiler of the Tribunal</P><P>Edited by - abaraxas on 03/22/2002  14:35:32</font></td>

